    "Condition : 1 - Approved Plans - The development hereby permitted shall be carried out in accordance with the following approved plans: Site location plan and drawings 51345-AEL-CXX-ZZ-PL-K-10001, 4A-0100-103 Rev C,  4A-0100-104 Rev C &, 4A-0100-114 Rev B",
